I humbly request the Court's consideration of the mitigating factors present in this case. I understand that this incident is an exception to my character and I am genuinely remorseful for my actions. With the lessons learned from this experience, I am dedicated to reassessing my priorities and emphasizing the importance of responsible driving.

Thank you, Your Honor, for your time and consideration. I accept full accountability for my actions and I sincerely hope that the Court will take into account my genuine remorse and my ongoing commitment to contribute positively to society.

